Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.85,0:26:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭要辭職了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.58,0:26:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.66,0:26:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.85,0:26:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才要謝謝你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.90,0:26:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.27,0:26:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位夫人 承蒙照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.35,0:26:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 能把最後的蛋給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.68,0:26:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春乃 成功了 我終於成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.65,0:27:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.98,0:27:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.32,0:27:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家來盡情吃蛋蓋飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.76,0:27:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明年還會再來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.79,0:27:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭候光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.03,0:27:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛西婭還能來的話 請一定要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.32,0:27:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.02,0:27:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼又要拜託你了哦 炸蝦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.69,0:27:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是摩托車的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.62,0:27:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.79,0:27:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到春乃摩托車的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.88,0:27:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.76,0:27:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 大家保重
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.13,0:27:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.45,0:27:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 請一定要再……
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.37,0:27:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 下次 下次我去見辛西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.68,0:28:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.45,0:28:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是很短的一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.72,0:28:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借助眾多他人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.03,0:28:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想瞭解更多未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.74,0:28:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點喜歡有這種想法的自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.38,0:28:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芋頭丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.66,0:29:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再會
